  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="final-cta-orb"></div>
    <div class="final-cta-inner">
      <h2>Your Transformation<br/>Starts Now</h2>
      <p>Stop letting your emotions run the show. Get all 6 books instantly and start building the emotional mastery you deserve.</p>

      <div style="margin-bottom:32px;">
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" onclick="checkoutBundle()">
          🛒 Get All 6 Books — $29
        </button>
